nodes.text: Kem Stor Ai was a planet located in the Tennuutta sector of the Mid Rim.

Kem Stor Ai talked of war with the planet Murkhana during the turmoil of the Second Galactic Civil War. The eruption of a conflict between the two worlds was of great concern for the Verpine who thought that Murkhana could use this conflict to attack the Roche asteroid field.
